title: Elegant Decor Colorado Log Cabin Cotton Patchwork Quilt Collection (Queen Quilt 90" W x 90" L)
description: Give your room a rustic makeover with the Colorado Cabin Patchwork Quilt. This handcrafted cotton quilt features an intriguing pattern with printed florals, leaves, mini stars, and hearts along with solid color bands. Colors include shades of white, dark blue, light cream, dark beige, sage, russet, burgundy, khaki, and chocolate. Quilt has a vermicelli-quilted background. Back has a mini floral print on eggshell. Quilt fill is cotton. Machine washable. Imported.
